data.description: Beautiful Borgata on large golf course lot on Granite Falls North #13. This one has it all. 2 bdrm, 2 bath + den w/Murphy bed. Newer gas stove (2020). Reverse osmosis. Gas fireplace. New fans 2022. Tile floors and new carpet in bdrms. Bose surround sound inside & patio. Central vac. Laundry has newer washer/dryer (2020) & utility sink. Security doors front & back patio. Sparkling pool. Expanded patio w/BBQ island. 3 car expanded length garage with built-in cabinets and back door exit. House painted outside 2018, inside 2023. 9,200 sq.ft. Casita-approved lot. HVAC 2012, water heater 2016. Fence painted 2020. Assumable solar lease with fixed pymt. This is a MUST SEE!
